<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV42">
<l>vaṉkāṟ ṟaṟaiya voruṅkē maṟintu kiṭantalarnta</l>
<l>meṉkāṟ kamalat taṭampōl polintaṉa maṇṇumviṇṇu</l>
<l>meṉkāṟ kaḷaviṉmai kāṇmiṉeṉ pāṉottu vāṉimirnta</l>
<l>taṉkāṟ paṇintaveṉ pālempi rāṉtaṭaṅ kaṇkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like a tank of soft-stalked lotuses in bloom, lying down altogether</l>
<l>as the strong wind gushes [at them],  they flourished – the broad eyes</l>
<l>of my lord [looking] at me, humbly at his feet, that had stretched out to the sky as if he said:</l>
<l>“look how to my feet earth and sky have no measure!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
